		<p><strong>Erika Suffern</strong> is an associate editor at the MLA. She received a BA from Bard College and an MA from the University of Delaware and has ten years of editorial experience. Before joining the MLA staff in 2016, she was associate director of the Renaissance Society of America and managing editor of its journal, <em>Renaissance Quarterly</em>.</p>
